<BaseLayout title="Supporters">
  <article class="article">
    <h1>Supporters</h1>
  <p>Learn more about our valued supporters.</p>
  <p>Outside is one of the few specialist outdoor equipment retailers left in the UK, offering expert advice and a wide range of equipment for rock climbing, mountaineering, and hill walking. They also have a strong online shop for those who can’t visit the Peak District, though many do for the personal touch the store provides. Outside has a long heritage in the industry, and the Trustees believe their commitment to recognising the shared history of climbing and its equipment aligns perfectly with the work of the MHT.</p>
  <h2>Trustees, Staff, Patrons &amp; Advisors</h2>
  <p>A diverse and enthusiastic team are ensuring that mountain heritage is protected for now and for the future. We're a small team but we've got big ambitions.</p>
  </article>
